Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
83 Whatley Crescent is positioned in the heart of the Bayswater Town Centre – a vibrant emerging TOD precinct.

Michael Milne and Ben Younger of CBRE, are pleased to represent this freestanding property sold via Public Auction.

PUBLIC AUCTION, HELD ON-SITE FRIDAY 20 JULY 2018 AT 11.00AM 

•	83 Whatley Crescent is located in the heart of the Bayswater Town Centre Core
•	Directly opposite Train Station, providing convenient access to the Perth CBD
•	Prominent strategic position flanked by an IGA Supermarket and Bayswater Post Office

•	Freestanding existing 335sqm* two storey buildings, viable for versatile ongoing uses
•	Potential for commercial, retail, food, restaurant, medical, health, fitness and much more. 
•	Generous parking options on-site and in immediate surrounds
•	Freehold 491sqm* land footprint with rear Right of Way Access
•	New 2018 planning framework permits 4 – 5 storeys mixed use development

SUITABLE FOR INVESTMENT, OWNER OCCUPATION AND REDEVELOPMENT

To obtain further information, contact the exclusive CBRE selling agents

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: SOLD BAYSWATER TOWN CENTRE LOCATION | OPPOSITE TRAIN STATION

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This is a brand new building with completion due April-May 2021, property features as follows:

- 2,310 sqm total land area
- 1,645 sqm total floor area
- 117 sqm ground floor office
- 117 sqm first floor office
- 52 sqm mezzanine storage area with concrete slab
- 1,359 sqm high truss warehouse
- Two 5m x 5m electric heavy duty roller shutters to warehouse
- Approx 398 sqm separate yard / lock up area with 6m x 6m electric roller shutter
- 8 - 8.5m high truss to warehouse
- Ground floor shower x2
- Ducted air conditioning to office areas & lunchroom
- Carpet tiles to office areas
- NBN connection
- Stone benchtops to kitchen and toilet vanities
- Ultracore G2 cladding to office facade
- 19 marked car bays includes allowance for FFL Storage to become Office with sufficient bays
- Landscaping
- 1800mm black Garrison secure fencing with automatic sliding gate
